snippet: The killings came after a barrage of car-bomb blasts and suicide bombings rocked Baghdad and two northern Iraqi communities on Thursday, the authorities said.
abstract: Barrage of car-bomb blasts and suicide bombings rock Baghdad and two northern Iraqi communities, killing at least 61 people; bulk of blasts strike in mainly Shiite parts of Baghdad.
lead_paragraph: The killings came after a barrage of car-bomb blasts and suicide bombings rocked Baghdad and two northern Iraqi communities on Thursday, the authorities said.

headline.main: Iraq: Blasts Kill at Least 61 People
headline.print_headline: Iraq: Blasts Kill at Least 61 People
